Value: Rafaella Resources Limited, explores for and develops tungsten and tin projects in Spain; and nickel, cobalt, copper, and gold projects in Canada. The company primarily owns a 100% interest in the Santa Comba project in Galicia, Spain; the McCleery exploration project in the Yukon Territory, Canada; and Midrim and Laforce projects located in the Quebec Province, Canada. Rafaella Resources Limited was incorporated in 2017 and is based in Brisbane, Australia.
